  <h2 class="header_b">The next chapter</h2>
  <p class="common-margin">As our winery grows, so too do our ranges. 2010 saw the release of our Sparkling Sauvignon Blanc, as well as the Brancott Estate Letter Series ‘B’ Late-Harvest Sauvignon Blanc, one of the few Marlborough Sauvignon Blanc dessert wines on the market. Because our home is important to us, we also launched the Brancott Estate Living Land organic range, with a portion of sales going towards saving the endangered New Zealand falcon. And our signature Marlborough Sauvignon Blanc continues to hold its own worldwide with a flurry of awards and accolades, including the top spot on Wine.com's 2016 Top 10 List.
  </p>
